        <section class="hero">
            <h1>About CloyMusic</h1>
            <p>More than just a music streaming service — we’re a movement driven by sound, soul, and technology.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="our-mission">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To revolutionize how people discover, listen to, and interact with music. We believe in building a future where every artist is heard and every listener finds their perfect soundtrack.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="our-story">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>CloyMusic started in a small apartment with a group of friends and a big dream: to make music accessible and meaningful again. What began as a passion project has now become a platform trusted by millions. From beta testing to breaking industry barriers, our journey has always been about innovation, integrity, and inclusion.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="values">
            <h2>What We Believe</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Artist First:</strong> We support creators by giving them tools, data, and fair monetization.</li>
                <li><strong>Listener Centric:</strong> Personalization is at our core — every playlist, every suggestion is curated just for you.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Driven:</strong> Music connects people. We provide spaces where artists and fans meet, talk, and grow together.</li>
                <li><strong>Tech-Powered:</strong> We invest in AI, immersive audio, and seamless UX to push music forward.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

